Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:26.38,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(100,100)}命運匆匆 吾等不從
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:26.38,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(100,100)}運命に　従順に
